targets.rawSql: SELECT timestamp as time, count() as audit_logs_count FROM "vault"."auditlogs" WHERE ( time >= $__fromTime AND time <= $__toTime ) GROUP BY time ORDER BY time ASC LIMIT 5000
SELECT timestamp as time, count() as operational_logs_count FROM "vault"."operation" WHERE ( time >= $__fromTime AND time <= $__toTime ) GROUP BY time ORDER BY time ASC LIMIT 5000

SELECT time, remote_ip, count_operation
FROM
(
  SELECT 
    timestamp as time, 
    log.request.remote_address as remote_ip, 
    count() as count_operation 
  FROM "vault"."auditlogs" 
  WHERE 
    ( time >= $__fromTime AND time <= $__toTime and log.type == 'response' ) 
  GROUP BY time, remote_ip 
  ORDER BY time, count_operation ASC
)
WHERE count_operation > 100

panels.title: Remote addresses with over 100 operations per second

targets.rawSql:
SELECT time, namespace, count_operation
FROM
(
  SELECT 
    timestamp as time, 
    log.request.namespace.id as namespace, 
    count() as count_operation 
  FROM "vault"."auditlogs" 
  WHERE 
    ( time >= $__fromTime AND time <= $__toTime and log.type == 'response' ) 
  GROUP BY time, namespace 
  ORDER BY time, count_operation
)
WHERE count_operation > 50

targets.rawSql:
SELECT time, path, count_operation
FROM
(
  SELECT 
      timestamp as time, 
      log.request.path as path, 
      count() as count_operation 
  FROM "vault"."auditlogs" 
  WHERE 
    ( time >= $__fromTime AND time <= $__toTime and log.type == 'response' ) 
  GROUP BY time, path 
  ORDER BY time, count_operation ASC
)
WHERE count_operation > 10

targets.rawSql: SELECT timestamp as time, count() as total FROM "vault"."auditlogs" WHERE ( time >= $__fromTime AND time <= $__toTime and log.type == 'response' ) GROUP BY time ORDER BY time ASC LIMIT 5000

SELECT timestamp as time, count() as total_write FROM "vault"."auditlogs" WHERE ( time >= $__fromTime AND time <= $__toTime and log.type == 'response' and (log.request.operation == 'create' or log.request.operation == 'update' or log.request.operation == 'delete')) GROUP BY time ORDER BY time ASC LIMIT 5000

SELECT timestamp as time, count() as total_read FROM "vault"."auditlogs" WHERE ( time >= $__fromTime AND time <= $__toTime and log.type == 'response' and (log.request.operation == 'read' or log.request.operation == 'list')) GROUP BY time ORDER BY time ASC LIMIT 5000

targets.rawSql: SELECT timestamp as time, log.request.operation as operation, count() as count_operation FROM "vault"."auditlogs" WHERE ( time >= $__fromTime AND time <= $__toTime and log.type == 'response' ) GROUP BY time, operation ORDER BY time ASC LIMIT 5000

SELECT 
  timestamp as time, 
  message.level as level, 
  count(message.level) count_level
FROM "vault"."operation" 
WHERE 
  ( time >= $__fromTime AND time <= $__toTime and message.hostname == 'vault-n1.openlab.net') 
GROUP BY time, level 
ORDER BY time ASC
